    <text><body>
            <div type="writingSession" n="1">
                <pb n="1r"/><p>
                    <note hand="https://edition-humboldt.de/addressee" place="mTop">envoyer le pié de lunette zur
                            See<supplied cert="high">.</supplied>
                        <lb/><choice>
                            <orig>Ecrivez</orig>
                            <reg>Écrivez</reg>
                        </choice> si quelqu’un a vu <choice>
                            <orig>a</orig>
                            <reg>à</reg>
                        </choice>
                        <placeName ref="https://edition-humboldt.de/H0008129 https://www.geonames.org/2988507">Paris</placeName>
                        <lb/><bibl corresp="https://edition-humboldt.de/RIUKP4EA"><choice>
                                <orig>le</orig>
                                <reg>les</reg>
                            </choice>
                            <choice>
                                <orig>Molecules</orig>
                                <reg>Molécules</reg>
                            </choice> de <persName ref="https://edition-humboldt.de/H0003693 http://d-nb.info/gnd/118674455">Brown</persName></bibl> et ce que
                        l’on<lb/>en dit</note>
                </p>
                <p><ref xml:id="f1e1162d-dcc5-4acd-a116-2ddcc51acd67" corresp="#b54d8a26-b745-439f-8d8a-26b745739f90" type="editorialNote">Je Vous supplie cher <lb/>ami, de commander <lb/>chez <orgName ref="https://edition-humboldt.de/H0995577">Chevalier</orgName> un <lb/><hi rendition="#u">microscope</hi> semblable <lb/>aux derniers qu’il <lb/>a <choice>
                                <sic>envoyé</sic>
                                <corr cert="high">envoyés</corr>
                            </choice> ici, mais <lb/>par la poste adressé <lb/><choice>
                                <orig>a</orig>
                                <reg>à</reg>
                            </choice>
                            <choice>
                                <abbr>Mr</abbr>
                                <expan>Monsieur</expan>
                            </choice>
                            <persName ref="https://edition-humboldt.de/H0004550 http://d-nb.info/gnd/104268190"><hi rendition="#u">Link</hi></persName>.</ref><note xml:id="b54d8a26-b745-439f-8d8a-26b745739f90" corresp="#f1e1162d-dcc5-4acd-a116-2ddcc51acd67" type="editorial">Vgl. Humboldts <ref target="https://edition-humboldt.de/H0016735">Schreiben
                                an Christian Gottfried Ehrenberg, [Berlin, nach September
                            1828</ref>] zum selben Sachverhalt.</note>
                    <note hand="#author" place="left"><hi rendition="#uu"><persName ref="https://edition-humboldt.de/H0004550 http://d-nb.info/gnd/104268190">Link</persName></hi></note> Faites <lb/>le payer <choice>
                        <orig>a</orig>
                        <reg>à</reg>
                    </choice>
                    <persName ref="https://edition-humboldt.de/H0004453 http://d-nb.info/gnd/116918241">Leo</persName> mais <lb/><choice>
                        <sic>recommander</sic>
                        <corr cert="high">recommandez</corr>
                    </choice> qu’on se <lb/>presse et que la <lb/>construction <choice>
                        <orig>mecanique</orig>
                        <reg>mécanique</reg>
                    </choice>
                    <lb/>et l’emballage des <lb/><choice>
                        <orig>pieces</orig>
                        <reg>pièces</reg>
                    </choice> soyent moins <lb/>mauvaisses. Observez <lb/>l’effet de ma lettre
                    <lb/>sur <persName ref="https://edition-humboldt.de/H0004414 http://d-nb.info/gnd/118779249">Legendre</persName><supplied cert="high">.</supplied> Je Vous <lb/>embrasse tendrement<supplied cert="high">.</supplied>
                </p>
               <closer><signed>Ht<pb n="1v"/></signed>
